Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到目标了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你绝对逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了  不行啊  老大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,面对联邦搜查官  这艘破船…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都这时候了还抱怨个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好  我不说第二遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甩掉它赶紧逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加老大  我肚子饿了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能把这家伙吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  巴齐鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等这蠢货把飞船停了再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真气人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查官进入飞船内了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,费我这么大劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想必已经有所觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无视联邦搜查官的停船命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外加使用武器抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备徒刑50年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  基加在哪呢  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加和巴齐鲁斯在哪  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  他们逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  想想办法嘛  帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空间跳跃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:54.41,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,300)\fad(1000,0)}一加一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  辛苦了  小山本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小泽取  今天也很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对小山本的摄影技术我绝对放心  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午饭和小紫苑一起吃怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紫苑  就我和小山本就行了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家久等了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  紫苑  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次也拜托你了  仑仑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小紫苑虽然是个新人  但上电视后好受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太棒了  天然的外星人角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在网上好像也炒得很热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不过听说那之后就拒绝再上电视了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想看准时机出名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  好可爱啊  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为保存用必须买两本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑好萌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  小紫苑的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  这可是现在秋叶原第一人气偶像  小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你眼瞎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比我姐姐都大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  听好  偶像与年龄无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  啊  在看这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  一上高中就情窦初开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这不是外星人笨蛋角色小紫苑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说笨蛋角色太失礼了  早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫天然  天然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  今天也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做这些事真的有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呀  基加确实是在这个星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经半年了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按欧里奥特拉时间算…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  按地球时间算已经5个月25天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的搜查确实正稳步接近目标  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事得做到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入调查是很花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加已经混入了这个世界的演艺圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是依露玛给的情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的是阿留多人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从DNA情报来看没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗叫做地球的行星  只有LV6的低文明度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却有很多联邦来的偷渡者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冒充地球人在此生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然跑到这偏远的原始星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是意外觉得这里很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这种地方肯定会变成依露玛那样的老太婆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得真过分啊  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我看在同为阿留多人的份上协助你们的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  在联邦中也是相当有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可轮不到你这黄毛丫头来叫我老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来  帝托  今天的酬劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  就这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不作为有田紫苑好好赚钱的话  就要一辈子住在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力工作的  我很高兴扮演有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子就要给点奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫义贺的家伙好像不是这个星球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,义贺先生  马上就一年了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然很有耐心  可也差不多该有个结果了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出资者那边也说不过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的科学家水平太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,调查「硫加」的精炼法还需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且饵食越来越难弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是外星人竟然怕警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦的搜查官可能也在这个星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多外星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有趣所以赶紧把硫加养大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戈梅斯一定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待啊  好像比傀儡木偶更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  帝托  义贺那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才店里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接他的车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像受到演艺制片方的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来接他的人有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了  别跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上那辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(665,200)}{\fn@方正水柱_GBK}{\frz270\fs22\fad(200,0)}新人偶像连续失踪之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你绝对逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  就当没看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥的车果然最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  五档加速的完美设计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正久保他们好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有短信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs19}抱歉、明天秋叶原有活动，\N今晚和羽泽一起通宵排队去了！！\N你一个人去废弃旅馆探险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的离家少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别把目光躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,废墟探险？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又在干无聊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  像小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闹市里的废墟  或许是个不错的报道素材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  拉我一把嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  好大的霉味  脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有趣了  这鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,废墟  给人一种死去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  制造出来的东西一旦被人扔掉就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是小孩的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是写着「禁止入内」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着这么嚷嚷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里归帝国电视台所有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点出去就报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  这么拽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是那么重要的地方的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起  我们不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  小鬼们尽惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  说得那么拽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊  是我们不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你怎么总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来探险的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,废墟是因为没人使用才叫废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经不算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也不会在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,义贺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了  一直在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定让我家那孩子在帝国电视台演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是有田紫苑呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  您不记得我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑好伤心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  基加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖束手就擒的话只要关160年哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狂战士杀手  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想反抗的话最好有所觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了抓你特地跑到这偏僻的星球上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是积了一肚子火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管你  我可是很中意这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧  联邦的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才这下追加5年刑期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用相当便宜的傀儡木偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然身手有点生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切  依古西奥拉的阿留多人当对手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  他进行过肉体改造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样打得才起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没和搜查官战斗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在拍电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那边出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加那家伙  就是溜得快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  眼看就要捉到的时候是最危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正面热源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好险  好险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咳  打偏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着义贺  却发现不得了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,导电性高分子剑能轻易刺穿你的身体护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老实点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在拍电视
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咳  抓来用用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了  阿留多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊  这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这是我的手？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  帝托  想想办法  帝托…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的  好像做了个不得了的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  你要睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他们要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  你爸爸一个人什么也做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是调动工作  总之我会时常来看他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好相处啊  你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  到了来个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸他们搬走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就半年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐偶尔会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个了  今天做了个奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你的眼镜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好像视力突然变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽说瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戴了隐形眼镜的就直说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  早宫  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  休息了两天  医生说可以来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别硬撑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像也会很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早  千明  须藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,替换的手臂是从夏玛朗那里拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  硫加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要换地方了  戈梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然把那个的管理交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顾客可是利比大人  你可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奥拉的阿留多人搜查官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  羽津美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人住也不能松懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去突击检查的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就要开始一个人住了吗
